Class AbstractCrudService<T,ID>

java.lang.Object
mb.pso.issuesystem.service.AbstractCrudService<T,ID>
All Implemented Interfaces:
CrudService<T,ID>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdditionalAttributeService, AdditionalAttributeTypeService, ChatService, ClientService, DepartmentFeedbackService, EmployeeService, IssueAttributeService, IssueEmployeeService, IssueFeedbackService, IssueService, IssueStateService, IssueTypeService, MessageService, MessageStatusService, NotificationService, SubjectService, SuppressedChatService, UserService
public abstract class AbstractCrudService<T,ID> extends Object implements CrudService<T,ID>
Abstract service for basic CRUD operations. create(Object) prevents persisting entities with a provided id.

If the entity does not auto-generate IDs, this behavior should be overridden.
